  skillName: 18
  skillNameText: Superconduct
  skillDescription: Enemies frozen by 'Zeropoint Burst' also have <color=#5b7ccf>-50%
    DEF and RES</color> for equivalent duration.
  favorText: Modified version of the defroster, now weakens the structure of the
    frozen object while leaving all the ice and moisture intact. The problem is,
    how is it called a defroster if it can't defrost anything...
  skillDescriptionInShort: '''Zeropoint Burst'' now reduces the DEF and RES of frozen
    targets.'
