  OnSelectSFX: {fileID: 0}
  skillType: 1
  skillName: 13
  skillNameText: Rewinding Breeze
  skillDescription: During the duration of 'Evasion', <color=yellow>reflects all
    incoming attacks</color> toward self to nearby enemies. Reflected projectiles
    instead will be sent back to the attacker. The first successful reflection also
    heals self for <color=green>20% max HP</color>.
  favorText: ... Now, instead of letting it all out, try to keep the compressed air
    around you, and it will form a layer of protection that can deflect any incoming
    attacks. Want to try?
  skillDescriptionInShort: '''Evasion'' now deflects all incoming attacks. First
    deflection also heals self.'
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 0b0000000c00000024000000
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
