  SelectedLvlName: {fileID: 1560593613}
  SelectedLvlDescription: {fileID: 751680392}
  Descriptions:
  - Everything must lead to a new world.
  - "Ever since you left,\\nI\u2019ve been standing here,\\nholding our memories
    in my heart,\\nliving as though searching for something."
  - '"Mr. Patriot.\nStop making people cry.\nThese brimming eyes can no longer see..."'
  - 'She wipes the dust off the old stone, engraved on it are words from an era that
    has long gone:\n"Is just not my gote." '
  - Have no love, no future either.\nHave no heart, no sadness either.\nGot no home
    to return to, wandering aimlessly.\nLike a rolling stone, how does that feel?
  - The worst thing about dying is that you won't be able to see the sunset ever
    again.
  - There are many ways to fill up a blank canvas. Regardless of what you choose,
    as long as you do with with your own hands, passion, and creativity, it's all
    beautiful and admirable.\n<color=yellow>Swap cool-down is halved in this level.</color>
  - The present. Day and night. And even time. I will run through them all.\n<color=yellow>Your
    units have increased MSPD in this level.</color>\n<color=red>The 'Sudarim' are
    immune to damage from Originium Pollutions.</color>
  - Just burn them all down if you want.\nFrom above, you woudn't take any damage
    anyway.
  - Hold tight to the days we spent together,\nNever let them go.\n<color=yellow>Swap
    cool-down is halved in this level. And your units have greatly increased attributes.</color>
  - Won't you set him free?
  - The picture of such a day,\nIn words, I write them down and send to you.
  - Even the malice someone held,\nEven the nights of a nameless town,\nEven you,
    shut tightly away in yourself like this,\nI know I'll still remain connected.\nYeah,
    let's paint it white.
  - Even so, I still want to talk about the future,\nKeep shining faintly, until
    the day I burn out.
  ChallengeModes:
  - '''Hounds'' have greatly increased HP and ATK.'
  - Terrains and enemies will differ in places, and more enemies will appear.
  - Bloodboil Knightclub Elite's ability stacks twice as fast. All enemies have increased
    MSPD.
  - One Sentinel has their position changed and takes different route. All 'Sentinels'
    have increased MSPD.
  - '''Sentinel''''s alarm grants greatly increased ATK and MSPD. Enemies have their
    weights increased by 1.'
  - All enemies become immune to physical and magical damage. 'Originiutants' have
    increased ASPD.
  - Terrain and enemies will differ in places.
  - More 'Caustic Originium Spiders' will appear. One 'Sudaram' has different starting
    position.
  - Some 'Originiutants' will be replaced with 'Bloodboil Knightclub Elites'.
  - Enemies will try to steal the Mint Fumo instead.
  - When 'Shrouded Assassin''s [Toward Death] is triggered, additional enemies will
    appear.
  - '''Gloompincers'' have increased ASPD under shrouded zones. And all enemies have
    increased MSPD.'
  - Some 'Candles' will be placed beforehand. 'Knight Territory Hibernators' need
    to stay inside shrouded zones for longer to fall asleep, and have increased ATK
    and MSPD upon waking up.
  - '''Candle''''s illumination range is reduced. ''Sentinent Toys'' have greatly
    increased DEF and RES.'
  SecretDescriptions:
  - To my beloved Professor,\nI think it should be fairly chilly in Victoria by the
    time my letter makes it to you? I hope you and everyone else are doing fine.
  - First, I'd like to thank you for your previous reply. You've helped answer a
    lot of my doubts for me.
  - You encouraged me not to give up on my studies, even during my treatment here
    at Rhodes Island.
  - Even though being away from Victoria has made a lot of things inconvenient, there's
    still a replete library here, as well as seniors and veterans to depend on.
  - My days here have been more fascinating and wonderful than I expected, and I've
    gained a lot for it.
  - '"In seeking the truth, I willingly brave all hazard."'
  - I still know this maxim by heart. No matter how challenging, Professor, I'll
    never give up.
  - But I want everyone to be reassured.
  - I'll pay mind to my own health, and I won't force myself to take on further risks.
  - I hope Miranda's recovery goes as speedily as possible. If I get the chance,
    I'll be sure to return and visit her!
  - Please say hello to her for me!
  - Thank you for always looking out for me. I'll look out for myself at Rhodes Island,
    and continue my research...
  - '"I have it figured out now! No matter what, I''ll continue doing the research
    I want to do!"'
  - '"I still have so many things I''m curious about, so many phenomena I want to
    figure out... I won''t leave anything unfinished no matter the results!"'
