  skillType: 1
  skillName: 12
  skillNameText: Wind's Elegy
  skillDescription: During the duration of 'Evasion', enemies coming into contact
    with self takes physical damage equal to <color=#ff4545>100% ATK</color> and
    are <color=#2985FF>pushed</color> alongside with the dash.
  favorText: At sufficient speed, the air pressure is large enough to cause an impact.
    And if you compress it to minimize the contact surface, just like a wind blade...
    scary, isn't it?
  skillDescriptionInShort: '''Evasion'' damages collided enemies and pushes them
    away slightly.'
