  skillNameText: '''Anthem of the Wind'''
  skillDescription: 'For melee player: Every attack land shortens the cool-down of
    ''Evasion'' by <color=#ff9717>0.75 seconds</color>, every ''Evasion'' usage shortens
    the cool-down of ''Juggernaut'' by <color=#ff9717>4 seconds</color>, every ''Juggernaut''
    usage grants <color=#ffd61f>+12 ASPD</color>, <color=#5b7ccf>lasts 15 seconds</color>
    and stacks up to <color=yellow>6 times</color>. At max stacks, gains an additional
    <color=#00ffbf>+36% MSPD</color> and all effects are <color=yellow>doubled</color>.'
  favorText: Her book alone can only carry words, her arts unit alone is just a staff,
    her originium arts alone does not excel. But, combined them together, with a
    little more work, and even the wind will bow to her.
  skillDescriptionInShort: 'Melee player: Attack shortens ''Evasion'' CD, ''Evasion''
    shortens ''Juggernaut'' CD, ''Juggernaut'' grants a stacking ASPD. At max stacks,
    doubles the effect and has increased MSPD.'
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
