  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  OnSelectSFX: {fileID: 0}
  skillType: 1
  skillName: 47
  skillNameText: '''Field Researcher'''
  skillDescription: 'For ranged player: Self''s projectiles <color=yellow>ricochet</color>
    upon hitting the target (triggers up to <color=#5b7ccf>5 times</color>). When
    a projectile comes into contact with an environmental tile, it <color=yellow>carries
    the respective effect</color> and apply them upon hitting the target.'
  favorText: She always wanted to participate in more research projects, and if possible,
    prefers to do it by herself. But you can't be in all the places in the world,
    not when you're doing it alone.
  skillDescriptionInShort: Ranged player's projectiles can ricochet and absorb the
    effects of environmental tiles it comes into contact with.
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
