  skillName: 42
  skillNameText: High-performance Defroster
  skillDescription: Damaging frozen targets instantly <color=#5b7ccf>ends its effect</color>
    to deal bonus true damage equals to <color=#b1b1b1>10% of the target max HP</color>.
    Damage increases by <color=red>50% ATK</color> for every freeze remaining second
    (cap at <color=red>400% base ATK</color>).
  favorText: '''Device that can remove any moisture and ice in an instant, especially
    useful on frozen equipments.''\n- Despite that oddly specific use cases, she
    has put it in good uses a decent amount of times.'
  skillDescriptionInShort: Damaging frozen targets instantly ends its effect to deal
    bonus true damage, increasing by the freeze's remaining duration.
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
