  skillType: 1
  skillName: 28
  skillNameText: Carmina Burana
  skillDescription: '''Der Tag Neight Sich'' <color=#ff00ff>locks-on to</color> the
    nearest enemy within attack range. While locking on to a target, all bullets
    will <color=yellow>home toward them</color>, but its damage ramps down overtime
    (to a minium of <color=#5b7ccf>30% of the base damage</color>).'
  favorText: Her attention device didn't quite work for her. The good news is that,
    for some reasons, it worked wonder on projectiles!
  skillDescriptionInShort: '''Der Tag Neight Sich'' homes all its bullets toward
    the nearest enemy within range.'
  mutuallyExclusiveSkills: 1b0000001d0000002700000033000000
  Overlay: {fileID: 0}
